Software from mercurial repository changeset 14
from 

Matlab software.

simulate_c_information_measurement.m is main program used to program to simulate
bit error rate following method used by
Stenner, Gauthier, and Neifeld letters to nature, vol 425, p. 695-8, 2003,
but applied to an acoustic example.


Just use the dotest=1  parameters within 
simulate_c_information_measurement.m  to get results.





